'''Jedi scout''' was a title used by the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] to describe members of the [[Exploration Corps/Legends|Exploration Corps]] who specialized in traversing [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] to find new worlds and bring them into the fold of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

==Overview==
During the [[Mandalorian Wars]], Jedi scouts (particularly those who opposed the [[Jedi High Council/Legends|Jedi High Council's]] decision to remain neutral during the conflict) covertly made their way to the front lines to assist the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Republic Military/Legends|military]]. During the [[New Sith Wars]], with the Republic abandoning much of the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]], Jedi scouts were no longer identifying potential students in those regions. In the later stages of war, scouts sought [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitives]] to recruit into the [[Army of Light/Legends|Army of Light]] before the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] could discover their location. [[Torr Snapit]] was among their ranks.<ref name="JvS1" /> <ref name="Star Wars: Knight Errant: Influx">{{SWArchive|url=vault/books/knighterrant_influx/index.html|text=''Star Wars: Knight Errant: Influx''|int=Star Wars: Knight Errant: Influx}}</ref>

